parameters.lighteningLevel: The brightness level. The value ranges from 0.0 (original) to 1.0. This parameter adjusts the red saturation level.

parameters.smoothnessLevel: The sharpness level. The value ranges between 0 (original) and 1. This parameter is usually used to remove blemishes.

parameters.rednessLevel: The redness level. The value ranges between 0 (original) and 1. This parameter adjusts the red saturation level.
